      <title>OPEC 考虑增加供应之际，石油巨头提高产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/big-oil-dials-up-output-growth-just-as-opec-mulls-supply-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司和雪佛龙公司在石油巨头的财报季结束时公布了化石燃料产量的大幅增长——而此时，石油输出国组织及其盟友正准备增加全球市场的原油供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/big-oil-dials-up-output-growth-just-as-opec-mulls-supply-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 22:09:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
